# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:14
translate spanish reba1_2943183a:

    # "I sit down in the driver's seat and start the car, not yet decided on how I am going to spend the rest of my evening."
    "Me siento en el asiento del conductor y arranco el coche, sin haber decidido aún cómo voy a pasar el resto de la tarde."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:15
translate spanish reba1_ed1fbe56:

    # "Then my phone starts buzzing."
    "Entonces mi teléfono empieza a vibrar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:21
translate spanish reba1_36a0a4e9:

    # "I'm not sure who it is, but it's a local number."
    "No estoy seguro de quién es, pero es un número local."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:24
translate spanish reba1_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "¿Hola?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:25
translate spanish reba1_421c326c:

    # "Unknown" "Hi, is this [pcname]?"
    "Unknown" "Hola, ¿eres [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:26
translate spanish reba1_206fe9f8:

    # pc "Uh yes, who is this?"
    pc "Eh, sí, ¿quién es?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:28
translate spanish reba1_3f54ba94:

    # rb "Hey! This is Reba, the pretty gal you helped on the side of the road."
    rb "¡Hola! Soy Reba, la chica guapa a la que ayudaste en la cuneta."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:29
translate spanish reba1_514501a6:

    # pc "Oh yeah! Hey, how are you?"
    pc "¡Ah, sí! Hola, ¿qué tal estás?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:30
translate spanish reba1_b20d36aa:

    # rb "I'm pretty dang good. I bet you thought I weren't gonna call you, huh?"
    rb "Estoy muy bien. Apuesto a que pensabas que no te iba a llamar, ¿eh?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:31
translate spanish reba1_3a31a86c:

    # pc "I wasn't sure."
    pc "No estaba seguro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:32
translate spanish reba1_12c083c1:

    # rb "Well I wanted to invite you over for dinner."
    rb "Bueno, quería invitarte a cenar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:33
translate spanish reba1_f8d534ae:

    # pc "Tonight?"
    pc "¿Esta noche?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:34
translate spanish reba1_fb6d5a5d:

    # rb "Yeah, man. Right now."
    rb "Sí, tío. Ahora mismo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:38
translate spanish reba1_44a6bff6:

    # "Reba was calling me again."
    "Reba me estaba llamando otra vez."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:41
translate spanish reba1_bea5e8cb_1:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "¿Hola?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:42
translate spanish reba1_13d5d84f:

    # rb "Hey, [pcname]. It's Reba."
    rb "Hola, [pcname]. Soy Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:43
translate spanish reba1_e10d698c:

    # rb "Just wonderin' if you wanna come over for some dinner?"
    rb "Me preguntaba si te apetece venir a cenar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:46
translate spanish reba1_26c5da0f:

    # rb "Yay! I'll text you directions to my house okay?"
    rb "¡Genial! Te enviaré un mensaje con las indicaciones para llegar a mi casa, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:47
translate spanish reba1_9ef2f77e:

    # rb "It's out in the middle of nowhere, so just give me a call if you get lost."
    rb "Está en medio de la nada, así que llámame si te pierdes."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:48
translate spanish reba1_5f7c28c5:

    # pc "Alright."
    pc "De acuerdo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:49
translate spanish reba1_4d98be45:

    # rb "See you when you get here!"
    rb "¡Nos vemos cuando llegues!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:51
translate spanish reba1_baffae44:

    # rb "You busy? Alrighty, well I'll try you again some other night."
    rb "¿Estás ocupado? Vale, pues te volveré a llamar otra noche."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:52
translate spanish reba1_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Me parece bien."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:53
translate spanish reba1_62d03f6c:

    # rb "Alright, talk to you later, [pcname]."
    rb "Vale, hablamos luego, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:58
translate spanish reba1_96642d84:

    # rb "Oh really? Well alright then."
    rb "¿En serio? Bueno, pues vale."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:59
translate spanish reba1_31a3112c:

    # rb "I thought you were a good fella, but I guess Mama was right when she said that city-boys were assholes."
    rb "Pensaba que eras un buen chico, pero supongo que mamá tenía razón cuando decía que los chicos de ciudad eran unos capullos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:60
translate spanish reba1_97e52919:

    # rb "Bye, [pcname]."
    rb "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:62
translate spanish reba1_acd799d7:

    # "She hangs up. I guess that relationship isn't going anywhere else."
    "Cuelga. Supongo que esa relación no va a ir a ninguna parte."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:63
translate spanish reba1_e6e74926:

    # "Oh well. I'm not interested in her anyways. Already moved on."
    "Bueno, da igual. De todos modos, no me interesa. Ya he pasado página."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:68
translate spanish reba1_a0107be8:

    # "We hang up and she texts me not too long after with detailed directions using landmarks to get to her house."
    "Colgamos y, poco después, me envía un mensaje con indicaciones detalladas, utilizando puntos de referencia, para llegar a su casa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:69
translate spanish reba1_4b1ef2e9:

    # "It takes about 20 minutes of following her complicated instructions before I pull into a long driveway out in the middle of nowhere that leads up to a trailer house."
    "Tardo unos 20 minutos en seguir sus complicadas instrucciones antes de entrar en un largo camino de acceso en medio de la nada que conduce a una casa prefabricada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:70
translate spanish reba1_b44e99ff:

    # "I know it is her house because of that old truck that's parked out front. But there are several other vehicles too."
    "Sé que es su casa por esa vieja camioneta que está aparcada delante. Pero también hay varios vehículos más."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:72
translate spanish reba1_b23c5ca9:

    # "I park and step out, walking towards the front door."
    "Aparco y salgo, caminando hacia la puerta principal."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:76
translate spanish reba1_ebd5eabf:

    # "Before I take two steps, a crazed looking man with a gun rushes out the front door of the trailer and charges towards me."
    "Antes de dar dos pasos, un hombre de aspecto enloquecido con una pistola sale corriendo por la puerta principal de la caravana y se abalanza hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:77
translate spanish reba1_e2aed0f3:

    # "I nearly piss my pants right there."
    "Casi me meo en los pantalones allí mismo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:78
translate spanish reba1_d8766968:

    # "Man" "What'chu doin' on my property boy?"
    "Man" "¿Qué haces en mi propiedad, chico?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:79
translate spanish reba1_1939bcec:

    # pc "Uh Reba..."
    pc "Eh, Reba..."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:80
translate spanish reba1_be8f8d66:

    # "Man" "We dun want nun of yer kind out here, now git!"
    "Man" "¡No queremos a gente como tú por aquí, así que lárgate!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:81
translate spanish reba1_0976b26b:

    # pc "Okay I'm leaving, sorry! Don't shoot me."
    pc "Vale, me voy, ¡lo siento! No me dispares."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:86
translate spanish reba1_e495c8b9:

    # "The trailer door bangs open and Reba rushes down towards me."
    "La puerta de la caravana se abre de golpe y Reba sale corriendo hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:87
translate spanish reba1_cb77e722:

    # rb "Mickey! Put the dang gun down and quit scarin' my friend."
    rb "¡Mickey! Baja esa maldita pistola y deja de asustar a mi amigo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:88
translate spanish reba1_20066a90:

    # rb "[pcname], this is my brother Mickey. He's just being a dillweed."
    rb "[pcname], este es mi hermano Mickey. Solo está haciendo el tonto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:90
translate spanish reba1_45c24e71:

    # mk "Aw sis, I's just havin' sum fun wit' the city slicker."
    mk "Ay, hermana, solo me estaba divirtiendo un poco con el urbanita."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:91
translate spanish reba1_c189b955:

    # rb "You just get yer butt back inside. Food's almost done."
    rb "Vuelve ya mismo para dentro. La comida está casi lista."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:92
translate spanish reba1_52b573db:

    # mk "Yeah, yeah."
    mk "Sí, sí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:97
translate spanish reba1_7a9d2a35:

    # rb "Hey, [pcname]. Sorry if he scared ya. He's kind of a pain in the butt."
    rb "Oye, [pcname]. Siento si te ha asustado. Es un poco pesado."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:98
translate spanish reba1_803406e3:

    # pc "I'm okay, I think."
    pc "Estoy bien, creo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:100
translate spanish reba1_8cc849fe:

    # rb "Well, this is my house. I live here with Mickey and Mama."
    rb "Bueno, esta es mi casa. Vivo aquí con Mickey y mamá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:101
translate spanish reba1_757350b7:

    # rb "It ain't much, but..."
    rb "No es gran cosa, pero..."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:103
translate spanish reba1_d4356e5a:

    # rb "Well that's it. It just ain't much."
    rb "Bueno, eso es todo. Simplemente no es gran cosa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:104
translate spanish reba1_defbb0a2:

    # rb "Food's just about ready though. Come in and I'll introduce you to Mama."
    rb "Aunque la comida ya casi está lista. Entra y te presentaré a mamá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:106
translate spanish reba1_4b85c32b:

    # rb "Just a warning though. She can be a little... opinionated."
    rb "Pero te aviso. Puede ser un poco... testaruda."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:107
translate spanish reba1_a101af89:

    # pc "Uh... okay."
    pc "Eh... vale."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:110
translate spanish reba1_bb793b2d:

    # "I follow her into the trailer."
    "La sigo al interior de la caravana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:111
translate spanish reba1_16dd944d:

    # "If I had even been hungry to begin with, the smell of the place definitely diminishes my appetite."
    "Si es que tenía hambre para empezar, el olor del lugar definitivamente me quita el apetito."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:112
translate spanish reba1_fd88ca50:

    # "First there is the scent of the chili, which isn't bad, but then underneath that, there is this odor that seems to be a mix of cigarettes, sweat, and maybe cat piss?"
    "Primero está el aroma del chili, que no está mal, pero luego, debajo de eso, hay un olor que parece una mezcla de cigarrillos, sudor y ¿quizás pis de gato?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:116
translate spanish reba1_becbdc4b:

    # rb "Mama, this is that boy I was tellin' you about. The one who helped me out the other day."
    rb "Mamá, este es el chico del que te hablaba. El que me ayudó el otro día."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:117
translate spanish reba1_a67c0e9d:

    # ma "He looks a little scrawny."
    ma "Parece un poco flacucho."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:118
translate spanish reba1_91ba5d20:

    # rb "Be nice Mama. I think he looks mighty fine."
    rb "Sé amable, mamá. A mí me parece que está muy bien."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:119
translate spanish reba1_a0523121:

    # ma "I guess if you're into the skinny, hairless, type, he ain't a bad lookin' fella."
    ma "Supongo que si te gustan los delgados y sin pelo, no está nada mal."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:120
translate spanish reba1_2517c171:

    # ma "Nice to meet you, [pcname]. You can just call me Mama."
    ma "Encantada de conocerte, [pcname]. Puedes llamarme mamá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:121
translate spanish reba1_84e32e06:

    # pc "Nice to meet you too."
    pc "Encantado de conocerte también."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:124
translate spanish reba1_ea70c271:

    # "Reba walks over to the small kitchen area and stirs the chili pot."
    "Reba se dirige a la pequeña cocina y remueve la olla de chili."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:125
translate spanish reba1_c00a5321:

    # "I think about turning and running out the front door. The whole situation feels weird."
    "Pienso en dar media vuelta y salir corriendo por la puerta principal. Toda la situación me resulta extraña."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:126
translate spanish reba1_5ef6ebbf:

    # rb "I think it's done. Let's eat. Everybody sit at the table."
    rb "Creo que ya está listo. Comamos. Que todo el mundo se siente a la mesa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:128
translate spanish reba1_6f4092c5:

    # "I hesitantly sit at the table with Reba, Mickey, and Mama."
    "Me siento a la mesa con Reba, Mickey y Mama, un poco indecisa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:129
translate spanish reba1_9c99b88f:

    # "It's so awkward. I just want to finish eating and leave."
    "Es muy incómodo. Solo quiero terminar de comer y marcharme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:130
translate spanish reba1_8d8f56b3:

    # "At least the chili is good though. Reba can definitely cook."
    "Al menos el chili está bueno. Reba sabe cocinar de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:131
translate spanish reba1_c632cc77:

    # mk "This is sum good possum chili sis."
    mk "Este chili de zarigüeya está buenísimo, hermana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:132
translate spanish reba1_4f104cbe:

    # "And it's ruined."
    "Y ya está arruinado."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:134
translate spanish reba1_a6f874ce:

    # ma "So what do you do, [pcname]?"
    ma "¿A qué te dedicas, [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:135
translate spanish reba1_5354681b:

    # pc "I'm in college and I work as an assistant in a law office in town."
    pc "Estoy en la universidad y trabajo como asistente en un bufete de abogados de la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:136
translate spanish reba1_0af5cb0e:

    # mk "College boy AND a lawyer?"
    mk "¿Un universitario Y un abogado?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:137
translate spanish reba1_3562724d:

    # mk "You sure know how to pick 'em, Reba."
    mk "Vaya si sabes elegirlos, Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:138
translate spanish reba1_7d3b9e0f:

    # ma "I never liked college folk."
    ma "Nunca me ha gustado la gente de la universidad."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:139
translate spanish reba1_030d9e4f:

    # rb "You don't even know any college folk, Mama. I already told you that I want to go to college."
    rb "Ni siquiera conoces a nadie de la universidad, mamá. Ya te he dicho que quiero ir a la universidad."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:140
translate spanish reba1_ad161f61:

    # ma "Ain't got money for it baby."
    ma "No tengo dinero para eso, cariño."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:141
translate spanish reba1_08132159:

    # ma "Plus they'd just mess up your mind."
    ma "Además, solo te liarían la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:142
translate spanish reba1_e2adf491:

    # ma "College is full of foreigners, gays, and liberals."
    ma "La universidad está llena de extranjeros, gays y liberales."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:143
translate spanish reba1_047c977e:

    # "Alright, I'm done."
    "Vale, ya he tenido suficiente."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:146
translate spanish reba1_f0544559:

    # pc "Well it was nice to meet you all. Thanks for the dinner."
    pc "Bueno, ha sido un placer conoceros a todos. Gracias por la cena."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:147
translate spanish reba1_9410a81f:

    # pc "I'm just going to head out."
    pc "Me voy a marchar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:148
translate spanish reba1_9bc53580:

    # ma "What? We ain't done yet."
    ma "¿Qué? Aún no hemos terminado."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:149
translate spanish reba1_d2b96a92:

    # mk "Let him go, Mama. The little snowflake got triggered."
    mk "Déjalo ir, mamá. El pequeño copo de nieve se ha ofendido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:152
translate spanish reba1_e7215967:

    # "I ignore them and just walk out of the trailer."
    "Los ignoro y salgo de la caravana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:155
translate spanish reba1_fd740709:

    # "Reba runs out after me."
    "Reba sale corriendo tras de mí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:156
translate spanish reba1_fee9c8d9:

    # rb "[pcname], wait up! Please!"
    rb "[pcname], ¡espera! ¡Por favor!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:157
translate spanish reba1_dedb026e:

    # rb "I'm really sorry. This was a bad idea. I just wanted to do something nice for you and I thought my family would be okay."
    rb "Lo siento mucho. Esto fue una mala idea. Solo quería hacer algo bonito por ti y pensé que mi familia no tendría ningún problema."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:158
translate spanish reba1_3dd86291:

    # rb "Look [pcname], I know we don't really know each other well, but I like you."
    rb "Mira, sé que no nos conocemos muy bien, pero me gustas."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:159
translate spanish reba1_4cfc6b53:

    # rb "I don't really have any friends that are like you. You know... smart."
    rb "No tengo ningún amigo que sea como tú. Ya sabes... inteligente."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:160
translate spanish reba1_7f0ddb3b:

    # rb "Please don't write me off because of my family. I'm not like them, I promise."
    rb "Por favor, no me descartes por culpa de mi familia. No soy como ellos, te lo prometo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:162
translate spanish reba1_af6f3f2c:

    # rb "Can we please see each other again sometime? Somewhere else, away from my family?"
    rb "¿Podemos volver a vernos alguna vez? ¿En otro sitio, lejos de mi familia?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:169
translate spanish reba1_9305d4e7:

    # rb "Thank you."
    rb "Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:170
translate spanish reba1_db562963:

    # rb "Can I kiss you now?"
    rb "¿Puedo besarte ahora?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:173
translate spanish reba1_92da6f83:

    # "I lean in and kiss her lips."
    "Me inclino y le beso los labios."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:174
translate spanish reba1_4b266ba6:

    # "They are soft, warm, and still taste a bit like possum chili."
    "Son suaves, cálidos y aún saben un poco a chili de zarigüeya."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:176
translate spanish reba1_18d653d1:

    # rb "That was nice. I'm looking forward to seeing you again sometime, [pcname]."
    rb "Ha estado bien. Espero volver a verte alguna vez, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:177
translate spanish reba1_402e7bfc:

    # rb "Have a safe drive home, okay?"
    rb "Conduce con cuidado de vuelta a casa, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:178
translate spanish reba1_1daad8dd:

    # pc "Thanks. I'll see you later."
    pc "Gracias. Nos vemos luego."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:180
translate spanish reba1_97e52919_1:

    # rb "Bye, [pcname]."
    rb "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:184
translate spanish reba1_6579a61b:

    # "Well that had been one of the worst dates that I've ever been on, but I still like Reba."
    "Bueno, esa ha sido una de las peores citas que he tenido, pero Reba me sigue gustando."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:185
translate spanish reba1_51e64dde:

    # "I just hope I never have to deal with her family again."
    "Solo espero no tener que volver a lidiar con su familia nunca más."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:191
translate spanish reba1_4b628d5a:

    # rb "Okay then. I understand."
    rb "De acuerdo, entonces. Lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:192
translate spanish reba1_1f8eb4cf:

    # rb "Have a safe trip home."
    rb "Que tengas un buen viaje de vuelta a casa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:193
translate spanish reba1_97e52919_2:

    # rb "Bye, [pcname]."
    rb "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:195
translate spanish reba1_cf8d6396:

    # "She turns and walks back to her house, not looking back."
    "Se da la vuelta y camina de vuelta a su casa, sin mirar atrás."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:196
translate spanish reba1_1ee6d168:

    # "I get into my car and drive away, glad to be done with that date."
    "Me subo al coche y me voy, contento de haber terminado con esa cita."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba1.rpy:197
translate spanish reba1_09c105b2:

    # "Reba might be fine, but it just isn't worth it to have to deal with her family."
    "Puede que Reba esté bien, pero no vale la pena tener que lidiar con su familia."

translate spanish strings:

